Description: Powered by Frooition.com Haute stuff at cool prices Shop Categories CHANEL 2016 Gray Pearl Jumbo Classic Double Flap Bag Purse ~ I am breathless! Item Description I don’t remember seeing gray pearl before Chanel’s Gray Pearl Jumbo Classic Double Flap – and I am pretty sure I would recall it because I am in deep love! Coming from 2016 with a dustbag, box, and card, there is a little wear on the second flap and a small dent on the bottom, as well as a need for an airing. The antiqued silver chain and leather strap may be worn with a drop of twelve and a half inches or a crossbody twenty-two and a half inches. The first flap opens with a turn lock to a zipped pocket and slide pocket, then the second flap unsnaps to a slide pocket, before the matching leather lining with two slide pockets on the back wall, while the outside back has another slide pocket. Quilted Caviar always looks good to me, but this time…I am breathless!
